room_title: Escape room "Escape In Space" by 321 Escape Rooms in Melbourne
room_address: 5270 N US HWY 1 Palm Shores, FL 32940
room_description: The year is 3210 and you are part of an elite group of scientists who are traveling on the Exodus, a Prometheus Class Ship. While traveling home, your craft is in danger of an asteroid attack that will wipe out the whole ship. You and your crew now face the challenge of escaping Exodus in plenty of time to be away from the ship before the asteroid strikes.
